CardData.FlavorText: <line-height=100%><size=200%>T</size>he spiders squeal in fearful rage as you drive them away from the cocoon. You hear growled speech from within the webs, but cannot make out the words. Even so, it's clear that whomever is inside is very displeased.

Localization.Title: Open the Thrashing Cocoon
Localization.Text: Tear open the cocoon and reveal what is trapped inside
